text: "Mobile" is a song by Avril Lavigne. It was only released in Australia and New Zealand. ==Charts== "Mobile" was only released in Australia and New Zealand. "Mobile" started its chart position at #36 on the New Zealand Singles Chart, climbing up to #26 in its fifth week. The song was also released in South Africa as an airplay single.
